n32l4xx-hal
===========

A peripheral HAL for the NSING N32L4xx (N32L403 / N32L406) microcontroller
family, written in Rust.

Attribution
-----------

This crate is a fork/port of n32g4xx-hal:

    https://github.com/guineawheek/n32g4xx-hal

originally authored by Sparrowgrine and guineawheek. The N32L4xx port
retargets that work to a different chip family (NSING N32L4xx) and diverges
where the silicon differs from the N32G4xx (notably the GPIO alternate-function
model: N32L4xx uses per-pin AFL/AFH selection rather than the N32G4xx AFIO
remap-group mechanism).

